---
layout: default.njk
---

<style>
    h1 {
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 3em;
    }

    .inline-logo {
        width: 2em;
        height: 2em;
        vertical-align: middle;
        margin-right: 0.25em;
    }

    .content-container {
        max-width: clamp(5rem, 90%, 100rem);
        margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .intro {
        font-size: 2em;
        font-weight: bold;
        margin-top: 0.5em;
        color: navy;
        text-wrap: balance;
    }

    .contact-link {
        font-weight: bold;
    }

    .designs {
        display: flex;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        align-items: stretch;
        gap: 1rem;
    }

    .design {
        box-sizing: border-box;
        width: min(20rem, 100%);
        padding: 1.5rem 2rem;
        border-radius: 0.5rem;
        background-color: dimGrey;
        color: white;
    }

    .design h3 {
        margin-top: 0;
        text-align: center;
    }

    figure {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
    }

    figcaption {
        font-style: italic;
        text-align: center;
        margin-top: 0.5em;
    }

    footer {
        text-align: center;
        margin-top: 2em;
        font-size: 0.8em;
        color: grey;
    }

    @media screen and (max-width: 600px) {
        h1 {
            font-size: 2em;
        }
        .intro {
            font-size: 1.5em;
        }
    }
</style>

<h1>
    <img src="/img/logo.svg" alt="Tiny Little Logo" class="inline-logo"/>
    Tiny Little
</h1>
<div class="content-container">
    <p class="intro">
        Tiny Little is run by a local photographer who loves to capture beautiful scenes from nature
        and share them with the community.
    </p>
    <p>
        Interested in purchasing greeting cards to sell at your business?
        <a class="contact-link" href="mailto:test-setup-not-a-real-address@example.com">Send an email!</a>
    </p>
    <h2>Explore current designs</h2>
    <div class="designs">
        {% for id, design in designs %}
            <div class="design">
                <h3>{{ design.name }}</h3>
                <figure>
                    <img src="/img/{{ id }}.jpg" alt="{{ design.name }} photo on the front of a greeting card" style="max-width: 100%; height: auto;">
                    <figcaption>{{ design.description }}</figcaption>
                </figure>
            </div>
        {% endfor %}
    </div>
    <h2>Questions? Comments? Design ideas?</h2>
    <p>
        Please reach out via email to <a class="contact-link" href="mailto:test-setup-not-a-real-address@example.com">test-setup-not-a-real-address@example.com</a>.
    </p>
    <footer>
        <p>
            <a href="https://github.com/tiny-little/tiny-little.github.io/">Website source</a> | Unless otherwise noted, the contents of this website are copyright Â© 2025 "Tiny Little" and its operator(s). All rights reserved.
        </p>
    </footer>
</div>